reviewText: After my daily walks, I do one (of the three) 10 minute segment a couple times per week for added benefits of strengthening and balancing the lower muscle group area.  This is perfect for timecrunchers! Stephanie leads you through standing and floor work without any needed weights and you don't need a large area for the exercises.  Stephanie has a lovely voice to lead you through balance challenge focused movements for your glutes as well as your legs.  It doesn't get any easier, uncomplicated, and effective.

reviewText: These three workouts when combined create a very advanced and effective workout. I compare this DVD to the Brazil [...]Lift DVDs, because the moves in this video are almost as challenging and are creative. So if you don't want to spend the money on the Brazil videos from beachbody then get this video.I like challenging videos that offer fitness moves that aren't repeated in every other fitness DVD. This is a fun workout and very effective. I highly recommend it.
